<!ENTITY welcome.label "Welcome to Mozilla Archive Format!">
<!ENTITY welcome.para1.description "Thank you for installing MAF! Your Firefox is now capable of opening and saving complete web pages in single-file [i]web archives[/i], supporting both the [tt]MAFF[/tt] and [tt]MHTML[/tt] types.">
